WEBVTT

00:00.880 --> 00:02.560
The Eunuch has long served by Father's side

00:03.120 --> 00:04.160
As a son

00:04.320 --> 00:05.120
Wishing to show filial piety

00:07.480 --> 00:09.000
I must trouble the Eunuch

00:11.800 --> 00:12.920
A few days ago, His Majesty

00:12.920 --> 00:14.000
Felt his vision blurring

00:14.320 --> 00:15.920
Had the imperial physician prescribe eye medicine

00:16.480 --> 00:17.240
After taking it for a few days

00:17.560 --> 00:18.000
Today

00:18.120 --> 00:19.440
He no longer summons the physician

00:22.920 --> 00:23.600
Last night

00:23.760 --> 00:24.680
People from the Imperial City Guard

00:24.760 --> 00:26.200
Already came to see His Majesty

00:27.120 --> 00:28.360
Thank you, Eunuch Wen, for the reminder
